## AI TOOLS OVERVIEW

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

**📝 TEXT TO ANIMATION**
Type what you want and AI builds it:
• "Bouncing ball with shadow"
• "Cinematic title fade in"
• "Floating particles"
• "3D rotating logo"

**🎭 AUTO ROTOSCOPING**
Select an object – AI masks it frame by frame:
• People, animals, cars
• Complex hair and fur
• Transparent objects
• Moving backgrounds

**🎯 SMART TRACKING**
No more manual keyframes:
• Face tracking (expressions)
• Object tracking (position, scale, rotation)
• Camera tracking (3D scenes)
• Text tracking (follow moving objects)

**🎨 AI COLOR GRADING**
• Match color from reference image
• Auto cinematic LUTs
• Scene-aware correction
• Skin tone preservation

